name: WoundCareI10
title: Wound Care I10
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains procedures used for wound care.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had a procedure performed for wound care.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes representing  procedures  related to wound care  using the  ICD 10 PCS code system.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
